==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Politzerization
<hw>Po*litz`er*i*za"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>The act of inflating the middle ear by blowing
air up the nose during the act of swallowing; -- so called from
<person>Prof. <etsep>Politzer</etsep></person> of <city>Vienna</city>,
who first practiced it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Polive</ent>⟦br⟧
